Cut paste photo editor can create family photo in which absent person can be added.with photo editor user can create photo by pasting multiple photo over others as sticker.

Features :
⦁ Cut photo with background eraser: Auto eraser remove background fast and gives you photos you can paste on any background.

⦁ Text on photo: We provide advanced text editor to add text on photos or convert cut photos into text. We include various fonts, textures, and advanced text styles.

⦁ Photo filters: Create awesome effects with photo filters including multiple of photo filters. Tools include transform features like rotate photo vertical and rotate photo horizontal.

⦁ Sticker and emoji: Doggy face for switch your face for free and create smiley stickers to make your funny frame. Emoji smiles will make your photos more fun.

Disclaimer:
All images used in this app are collected from the web. If you own rights to any of the images, and do not wish them to appear here, please let us know and it will be removed as soon as possible.

If you like this app then rate it and review it and share this with your friends and family.

Thank you.
